0f4ng tin.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft trang tr\u00ed l\u00e0m t\u1eeb nh\u00f4m, pedal b\u1ecdc nh\u00f4m v\u00e0 b\u1eadc c\u1eeda \u1ed1p kim lo\u1ea1i. Tr\u00ean ph\u1ea7n t\u1ef1a l\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a gh\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eau th\u00eam ch\u1eef Sport. Trung t\u00e2m m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng 7 inch v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed \u0111a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-3846\" src=\"http:\/\/hyundai.w2steam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/hyundai-elantra-va-tucson-2019-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam-151-5.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 668px) 100vw, 668px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/hyundai.w2steam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/hyundai-elantra-va-tucson-2019-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam-151-5.jpg 668w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-2019-ra-mat-6-168x112.jpg 168w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-2019-ra-mat-6-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-2019-ra-mat-6-888x593.jpg 888w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-2019-ra-mat-6-24x16.jpg 24w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-2019-ra-mat-6-36x24.jpg 36w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-2019-ra-mat-6-48x32.jpg 48w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-2019-ra-mat-6-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-2019-ra-mat-6.jpg 959w\" alt=\"\" width=\"668\" height=\"446\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Chi\u1ebfc Elantra Sport \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng t\u0103ng \u00e1p 1.6L, cho c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 204 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i 6.000 v\u00f2ng\/ph\u00fat v\u00e0 Mo-men xo\u1eafn c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i 265 Nm trong d\u1ea3i v\u00f2ng tua 1.500 ~ 4.500 v\u00f2ng\/ph\u00fat. Xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb h\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 ly h\u1ee3p k\u00e9p 7 c\u1ea5p DCT.<\/p>\n<p>Elantra Sport v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng treo sau \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u0129a phanh sau l\u1edbn h\u01a1n nh\u1eb1m mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00e0 th\u00fa v\u1ecb h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-3848\" src=\"http:\/\/hyundai.w2steam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/hyundai-elantra-va-tucson-2019-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam-151-6.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 668px) 100vw, 668px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/hyundai.w2steam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/hyundai-elantra-va-tucson-2019-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam-151-6.jpg 668w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-Sport-2019-ra-mat-2-168x112.jpg 168w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-Sport-2019-ra-mat-2-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-Sport-2019-ra-mat-2-888x593.jpg 888w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-Sport-2019-ra-mat-2-24x16.jpg 24w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-Sport-2019-ra-mat-2-36x24.jpg 36w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-Sport-2019-ra-mat-2-48x32.jpg 48w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Elantra-Sport-2019-ra-mat-2-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/upl