9.jpg 668w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-2-168x112.jpg 168w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-2-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-2-888x593.jpg 888w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-2-24x16.jpg 24w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-2-36x24.jpg 36w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-2-48x32.jpg 48w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-2-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-2.jpg 959w\" alt=\"\" width=\"668\" height=\"446\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng ch\u00ednh c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 full LED v\u1edbi 5 tinh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7y tinh ch\u1ee9a h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e8n nh\u1ecf \u1edf m\u1ed7i c\u1ee5m, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 cao \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi cung c\u1ea5p l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1t khi v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng y\u1ebfu. B\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi, \u0111\u00e8n s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thu nh\u1ecf, c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao quanh b\u1edfi d\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e8n LED h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef L. Lazang Tucson 2019 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1edbi theo phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi 3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc: 17, 18 v\u00e0 19 inch (b\u1ea3n Turbo).<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-3851\" src=\"http:\/\/hyundai.w2steam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/hyundai-elantra-va-tucson-