th: 668px) 100vw, 668px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/hyundai.w2steam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/hyundai-elantra-va-tucson-2019-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam-151-11.jpg 668w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-4-168x101.jpg 168w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-4-768x462.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-4-888x535.jpg 888w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-4-24x14.jpg 24w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-4-36x22.jpg 36w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-4-48x29.jpg 48w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-4-600x361.jpg 600w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-4.jpg 960w\" alt=\"\" width=\"668\" height=\"402\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Hyundai Tucson 2019 Facelift s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1edbi sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng g\u00e2n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u cao c\u1ea5p. Nguy\u00ean l\u00fd thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf HMI (Human Machine Interface) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi gi\u00fap Tucson s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, ti\u1ec7n nghi nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1ea5t trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-3840\" src=\"http:\/\/hyundai.w2steam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/hyundai-elantra-va-tucson-2019-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam-151-12.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 668px) 100vw, 668px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/hyundai.w2steam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/hyundai-elantra-va-tucson-2019-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam-151-12.jpg 668w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-5-168x112.jpg 168w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-5-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-5-888x593.jpg 888w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-5-24x16.jpg 24w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-5-36x24.jpg 36w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-5-48x32.jpg 48w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-5-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-5.jpg 959w\" alt=\"\" width=\"668\" height=\"446\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t l\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng trung t\u00e2m 8 inch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng Fly-Monitor. V\u1edbi Fly monitor, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quan s\u00e1t tr\u1ef1c quan h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00fap b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft, n\u00fat b\u1ea5m n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. X\u00e9t t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Tucson 2019 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Apple Carplay, b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb d\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec7 tinh d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed quen thu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 Bluetooth\/Radio FM\/AM\/AUX\/USB h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 file \u0111a \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng. B\u1ed9 x\u1eed l\u00ed Arkamys Premium Sound v\u1edbi DAC SAF775X gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 k\u0129 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 chu\u1ea9n 24bit\/192khz \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u00e2m thanh cao c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi 6 loa.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-3839\" src=\"http:\/\/hyundai.w2steam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/hyundai-elantra-va-tucson-2019-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam-151-13.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 668px) 100vw, 668px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/hyundai.w2steam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/hyundai-elantra-va-tucson-2019-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam-151-13.jpg 668w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-6-168x112.jpg 168w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-6-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-6-888x593.jpg 888w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-6-24x16.jpg 24w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-6-36x24.jpg 36w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-6-48x32.jpg 48w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-6-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-6.jpg 959w\" alt=\"\" width=\"668\" height=\"446\" \/><\/p>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng trang b\u1ecb ti\u1ec7n nghi th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng 2 v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp, c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 tr\u1eddi to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh Panorama, c\u1ed1p \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, \u0111\u00e8n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng,\u2026Tucson \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb th\u00eam s\u1ea1c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y chu\u1ea9n Qi, g\u01b0\u01a1ng chi\u1ebfu h\u1eadu ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00f3i t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng ECM.<\/p>\n<p>Tucson 2019 Facelift ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 3 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00f3m \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-3838\" src=\"http:\/\/hyundai.w2steam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/hyundai-elantra-va-tucson-2019-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam-151-14.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 668px) 100vw, 668px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/hyundai.w2steam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/hyundai-elantra-va-tucson-2019-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam-151-14.jpg 668w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-7-168x112.jpg 168w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-7-888x592.jpg 888w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-7-24x16.jpg 24w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-7-36x24.jpg 36w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-7-48x32.jpg 48w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-7-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/hyundailevanluong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Hyundai-Tucson-2019-ra-mat-7.jpg 960w\" alt=\"\" width=\"668\" height=\"445\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 Turbo phun x\u0103ng tr\u1